		<h2 class=" text-2xl text-primary ">Company History</h2>
			<p class="leading-loose">
	Edward M. Caspers founded Caspers Construction in Fullerton, CA in 1968 and incorporated in 1976. Possessing an eye for craftsmanship and detail, he created a company specializing in refined additions and custom homes. He achieved his goals for over 30 years before passing the leadership role to his son, Edward A. Caspers.
	In 2001, Edward A. Caspers opened the doors of Caspers Construction Corporation in Long Beach, CA where he has continued the tradition of excellence in building, client relations and the timely completion of custom additions and custom homes.</p>

